column6:
Graphic design is the creation of visual compositions to communicate ideas and solve problems through typography, imagery, colour and form. This capability covers the provision of graphic design (visual content creation) services including publication graphic design, motion graphic design and marketing/promotional graphic design to EP clients for internal communication purposes.  
 
The capability exists to provide a wide range of professional graphic design products and graphic design advice to EP clients including:
 * Multi-channel digital publishing: virtual backgrounds, animations, interactive PDFs, infographics, eTemplates, ePosters, illustrations, etc.;
 * Print products: brochures, posters, visual expos, stationery etc.;
 * Graphic design consultancy;
 * Ready-to-use photos and graphics.

